query: SELECT a.id, a.title, a.createdAt, COUNT(DISTINCT t.title) as unique_tracks, COUNT(t.id) as total_tracks FROM albums a LEFT JOIN tracks t ON a.id = t.albumId GROUP BY a.id ORDER BY a.createdAt ASC
